content:
@PaulTBackes Thanks for sharing your story. We can't wait to hear how this semester goes. 

It's student stories like yours that reaffirm our decision to keep learning flexible during this time, offering in-seat, virtual and online classes. 

Keep up the good work! #WeAreCC

Phoenix Public Library is hosting a virtual art exhibit in February 2021 to celebrate Black History Month! Young artists in grades K-12 are invited to draw an important person or event celebrating the African American experience.

